{"label":"Mal 3:5","book":"Mal","chapter":3,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"What will you do on the day of punishment"},{"kind":"text","text":" when devastation comes from far away?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Who will you run to for help?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Where will you leave your wealth?"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"There will be nothing to do"},{"kind":"text","text":" except crouch among the prisoners"},{"kind":"text","text":" or fall among the slain."},{"kind":"text","text":" In all this, his anger has not turned away,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and his hand is still raised to strike. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:25","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 9:12","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 9:17","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 9:21","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":21,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 5:25","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":25},{"label":"Is 9:12","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":12},{"label":"Is 9:17","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":17},{"label":"Is 9:21","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Woe to Assyria, the rod of my anger —"},{"kind":"text","text":" the staff in their hands is my wrath."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will send him against a godless nation;"},{"kind":"text","text":" I will command him to go"},{"kind":"text","text":" against a people destined for my rage,"},{"kind":"text","text":" to take spoils, to plunder, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 21:14","book":"2Ki","chapter":21,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 49:32","book":"Jer","chapter":49,"verse":32,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 7:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":7,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 26:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 29:19","book":"Ezk","chapter":29,"verse":19,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to trample them down like clay "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 22:43","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":43,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 18:42","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":42,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 26:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":11,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mc 7:10","book":"Mic","chapter":7,"verse":10,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the streets."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 21:14","book":"2Ki","chapter":21,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 49:32","book":"Jer","chapter":49,"verse":32},{"label":"Ezk 7:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":7,"verse":21},{"label":"Ezk 26:12","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":12},{"label":"Ezk 29:19","book":"Ezk","chapter":29,"verse":19},{"label":"2Sm 22:43","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":43},{"label":"Ps 18:42","book":"Psa","chapter":18,"verse":42},{"label":"Ezk 26:11","book":"Ezk","chapter":26,"verse":11},{"label":"Mc 7:10","book":"Mic","chapter":7,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But this is not what he intends;"},{"kind":"text","text":" this is not what he plans."},{"kind":"text","text":" It is his intent to destroy"},{"kind":"text","text":" and to cut off many nations."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For he says,"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Aren’t all my commanders kings?"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Isn’t Calno like Carchemish?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Isn’t Hamath like Arpad?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Isn’t Samaria "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:8","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" like Damascus? "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Cities conquered by Assyria"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 1:8","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Cities conquered by Assyria"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"As my hand seized the kingdoms of worthless images,"},{"kind":"text","text":" kingdoms whose idols exceeded those of Jerusalem and Samaria,"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and as I did to Samaria and its worthless images"},{"kind":"text","text":" will I not also do to Jerusalem and its idols?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 21:11","book":"2Ki","chapter":21,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 23:24","book":"2Ki","chapter":23,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 15:8","book":"2Ch","chapter":15,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Ch 24:18","book":"2Ch","chapter":24,"verse":18,"letter":"d"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 21:11","book":"2Ki","chapter":21,"verse":11},{"label":"2Kg 23:24","book":"2Ki","chapter":23,"verse":24},{"label":"2Ch 15:8","book":"2Ch","chapter":15,"verse":8},{"label":"2Ch 24:18","book":"2Ch","chapter":24,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But when the Lord finishes all his work against Mount Zion and Jerusalem, he will say, “I "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"LXX reads Jerusalem, he"},{"kind":"text","text":" will punish the king of Assyria for his arrogant acts and the proud look in his eyes.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 50:31","book":"Jer","chapter":50,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 50:31","book":"Jer","chapter":50,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"LXX reads Jerusalem, he"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For he said:"},{"kind":"text","text":" I have done this by my own strength"},{"kind":"text","text":" and wisdom, for I am clever."},{"kind":"text","text":" I abolished the borders of nations"},{"kind":"text","text":" and plundered their treasures; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 15:13","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 17:3","book":"Jer","chapter":17,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 20:5","book":"Jer","chapter":20,"verse":5,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" like a mighty warrior, I subjugated the inhabitants. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or I brought down their kings"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 22:48","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":48,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 15:13","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":13},{"label":"Jr 17:3","book":"Jer","chapter":17,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 20:5","book":"Jer","chapter":20,"verse":5},{"label":"2Sm 22:48","book":"2Sa","chapter":22,"verse":48}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or I brought down their kings"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"My hand has reached out, as if into a nest,"},{"kind":"text","text":" to seize the wealth of the nations."},{"kind":"text","text":" Like one gathering abandoned eggs,"},{"kind":"text","text":" I gathered the whole earth."},{"kind":"text","text":" No wing fluttered;"},{"kind":"text","text":" no beak opened or chirped."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Does an ax exalt itself"},{"kind":"text","text":" above the one who chops with it?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Does a saw magnify itself"},{"kind":"text","text":" above the one who saws with it?"},{"kind":"text","text":" It would be like a rod waving the ones who lift "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss; other Hb mss, Syr, Vg read the one who lifts"},{"kind":"text","text":" it!"},{"kind":"text","text":" It would be like a staff lifting the one who isn’t wood!"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Some Hb mss; other Hb mss, Syr, Vg read the one who lifts"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies"},{"kind":"text","text":" will inflict an emaciating disease"},{"kind":"text","text":" on the well-fed of Assyria,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and he will kindle a burning fire"},{"kind":"text","text":" under its glory."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Israel’s Light will become a fire,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and its Holy One, a flame. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 4:5","book":"Isa","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:24","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 47:14","book":"Isa","chapter":47,"verse":14,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" In one day it will burn and consume Assyria’s thorns and thistles. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 3:18","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":18,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 5:6","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 7:23–25","book":"Isa","chapter":7,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 9:18","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 27:4","book":"Isa","chapter":27,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 10:8","book":"Hos","chapter":10,"verse":8,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 4:5","book":"Isa","chapter":4,"verse":5},{"label":"Is 5:24","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":24},{"label":"Is 47:14","book":"Isa","chapter":47,"verse":14},{"label":"Gn 3:18","book":"Gen","chapter":3,"verse":18},{"label":"Is 5:6","book":"Isa","chapter":5,"verse":6},{"label":"Is 7:23–25","book":"Isa","chapter":7,"verse":23},{"label":"Is 9:18","book":"Isa","chapter":9,"verse":18},{"label":"Is 27:4","book":"Isa","chapter":27,"verse":4},{"label":"Hs 10:8","book":"Hos","chapter":10,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He will completely destroy"},{"kind":"text","text":" the glory of its forests and orchards"},{"kind":"text","text":" as a sickness consumes a person."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The remaining trees of its forest"},{"kind":"text","text":" will be so few in number"},{"kind":"text","text":" that a child could count them."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day the remnant of Israel and the survivors of the house of Jacob will no longer depend on the one who struck them, but they will faithfully depend on the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", the Holy One of Israel. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 1:4","book":"Isa","chapter":1,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The remnant will return, the remnant of Jacob,"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the Mighty God."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Israel, even if your people were as numerous"},{"kind":"text","text":" as the sand of the sea,"},{"kind":"text","text":" only a remnant of them will return. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 19:30","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":30,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 19:31","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":31,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezr 9:8","book":"Ezr","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezr 9:15","book":"Ezr","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 11:11","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":11,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 11:16","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 28:5","book":"Isa","chapter":28,"verse":5,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 37:31","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":31,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 37:32","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":32,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 46:3","book":"Isa","chapter":46,"verse":3,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:3","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":3,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 31:7","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":7,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:27–28","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":27,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"text","text":" Destruction has been decreed;"},{"kind":"text","text":" justice overflows."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 19:30","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":30},{"label":"2Kg 19:31","book":"2Ki","chapter":19,"verse":31},{"label":"Ezr 9:8","book":"Ezr","chapter":9,"verse":8},{"label":"Ezr 9:15","book":"Ezr","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"Is 11:11","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":11},{"label":"Is 11:16","book":"Isa","chapter":11,"verse":16},{"label":"Is 28:5","book":"Isa","chapter":28,"verse":5},{"label":"Is 37:31","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":31},{"label":"Is 37:32","book":"Isa","chapter":37,"verse":32},{"label":"Is 46:3","book":"Isa","chapter":46,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 23:3","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 31:7","book":"Jer","chapter":31,"verse":7},{"label":"Rm 9:27–28","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For throughout the land"},{"kind":"text","text":" the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies"},{"kind":"text","text":" is carrying out a destruction that was decreed."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore, the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies says this: “My people who dwell in Zion, do not fear Assyria, though they strike you with a rod and raise their staff over you as the Egyptians did. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"In just a little while my wrath will be spent and my anger will turn to their destruction.” "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies will brandish a whip against him as he did when he struck Midian at the rock of Oreb; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 7:25","book":"Jdg","chapter":7,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and he will raise his staff over the sea as he did in Egypt."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jdg 7:25","book":"Jdg","chapter":7,"verse":25}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"On that day"},{"kind":"text","text":" his burden will fall from your shoulders,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and his yoke from your neck."},{"kind":"text","text":" The yoke will be broken because your neck will be too large. "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit because of fatness; Hb obscure"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gn 27:40","book":"Gen","chapter":27,"verse":40,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 28:48","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":48,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 28:10","book":"Jer","chapter":28,"verse":10,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 30:8","book":"Jer","chapter":30,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lm 1:14","book":"Lam","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Gn 27:40","book":"Gen","chapter":27,"verse":40},{"label":"Dt 28:48","book":"Deu","chapter":28,"verse":48},{"label":"Jr 28:10","book":"Jer","chapter":28,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 30:8","book":"Jer","chapter":30,"verse":8},{"label":"Lm 1:14","book":"Lam","chapter":1,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit because of fatness; Hb obscure"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Assyria has come to Aiath"},{"kind":"text","text":" and has gone through Migron,"},{"kind":"text","text":" storing their equipment at Michmash."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They crossed over at the ford, saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":" “We will spend the night at Geba.”"},{"kind":"text","text":" The people of Ramah are trembling;"},{"kind":"text","text":" those at Gibeah of Saul have fled."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Cry aloud, daughter of Gallim!"},{"kind":"text","text":" Listen, Laishah!"},{"kind":"text","text":" Anathoth is miserable."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Madmenah has fled."},{"kind":"text","text":" The inhabitants of Gebim have sought refuge."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Today the Assyrians will stand at Nob,"},{"kind":"text","text":" shaking their fists at the mountain of Daughter Zion,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the hill of Jerusalem."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Look, the Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Armies"},{"kind":"text","text":" will chop off the branches with terrifying power,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the tall trees will be cut down,"},{"kind":"text","text":" the high trees felled."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Isa:10:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"He is clearing the thickets of the forest with an ax,"},{"kind":"text","text":" and Lebanon with its majesty will fall."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279540179}